    dc:description "FIGURES 66–74. Australoluciola spp. 66–71 Aus. fuscamagna sp. nov. holotype male (ANIC). 72–74 Aus. fuscaparva sp. nov. holotype male (ANIC). 66, 72 dorsal, 67 ventral; 68, 73 terminal abdomen with LO; 69, 70 aedeagus ventral (69) and left lateral; 71, 74 pronota, dorsal. These figures share scale lines 69, 70." ;
